## Database Management

```bash
# Start database
docker-compose up -d

# Stop database (keeps data)
docker-compose stop

# Stop and remove containers (keeps data)
docker-compose down

# Stop and delete all data
docker-compose down -v

# View logs
docker-compose logs -f
```

